lead_paragraph: Angel Di Maria bagged the winner as Paris St Germain beat Lille 2-1 to capture the French League Cup trophy for the third year in succession, and for a record sixth time, on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Di Maria Joy as PSG Land League Cup Trophy Again
headline.main: Di Maria Joy as PSG Land League Cup Trophy Again
